{"tid":353390,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次食日式秘魯菜.....","createTime":"2017-08-09T14:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T11:14:38.000Z","uid":104186,"like":1,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30f2b8dea22a06e6a004232d1a06ed6e71303ec7","tid":353390,"uid":104186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:15:14.000Z","msg":"原文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/findfindeateat/posts/1843290112352889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffindfindeateat%2Fposts%2F1843290112352889&d=C4m1Kk2qynx16K1dV7oruC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0faf11f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/findfindeateat/posts/1843290112352889</a><br />\n<br />\n秘魯菜夠特別，日式秘魯菜更加係聽都未聽過🙈<br />\n<br />\n上網搜一搜，由於曾經有好多日本人移居秘魯，因此發展出呢門咁特別嘅菜式，以酸辣為主，但係口味清新唔會有東南亞菜般嘅重口味。而同事味道層次感豐富之餘亦唔難食出好多其他地方菜式嘅風味。<br />\n<br />\nTokyolima 嘅Brunch Set，只限周末供應。話就話係Brunch，但份量多到嚇死人，4道前菜2道冷盤1道主菜加甜品，比擬一餐豐富晚餐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/221247_9f1f3e5f3b043277284a974c247c242d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F221247_9f1f3e5f3b043277284a974c247c242d.jpg&h=9465be94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭盤中先來嘅炸雞同冷麵沙律，好食但不算重點，喺度就唔多講了。然後嚟嘅沙律「T-3」，就好似佢形容咁係一道如颱風般刺激味蕾嘅菜式- 沙律入面用唔同嘅材料及調味做成多重口感，時而爽時而香脆，一時係醋汁味道然後又食到材料嘅甜味，啖啖驚喜，真係非常鐘意！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/221326_1fc632c25ea0f1e703e299c7866f95d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F221326_1fc632c25ea0f1e703e299c7866f95d7.jpg&h=7982bbbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/221326_7e5e1358d819a76934c5e0fd828b807c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F221326_7e5e1358d819a76934c5e0fd828b807c.jpg&h=a335149c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一道Lomo Saltado 係一味墨西哥tacos，用上超濃嘅薄荷醬，味道刺激未必人人受到，但換著我鐘意食呢隻醬汁嘅就覺得好爽了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/221343_57378926c9896e2578529945de6de767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F221343_57378926c9896e2578529945de6de767.jpg&h=440d2790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後兩款刺身H&amp;M 及 Ceviche Clasico - 前者係吞拿魚及油甘魚，特別在刺身豉汁加入柚子嘅酸甜味道，同樣開胃；後者係秘魯傳統菜，用極酸嘅醬汁格硬「醃熟」鮮鱸魚肉，但同時魚肉又不失刺身嘅鮮甜。呢道菜仲加入咗秘魯出名嘅Tiger's Milk，開頭以為係老虎奶咁犀利？原來係一種青檸及魚湯等混成嘅湯汁...... <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/221415_b30bcc37d30a0ce11d1acc7dcb200eac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F221415_b30bcc37d30a0ce11d1acc7dcb200eac.jpg&h=1dcea48d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/221415_cb1ba4c61664513927f3c2f649c98024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F221415_cb1ba4c61664513927f3c2f649c98024.jpg&h=af455c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實食完以上前菜已經好飽，不過仍然無減去我哋食主菜嘅胃口，因為真係好好食👍🏻加錢要咗一款Grilled Black Cod，燒魚扒又滑又鮮甜，不過有啲似香鮮醬嘅醬汁本人就覺得甜得滯，所以都係鍾意就咁食個魚多啲；而另一款煎牛扒Picanha，牛後腿肉牛味濃郁，外皮已煎到微濃嘅香脆口感，5成熟淋得嚟仍保留嚼勁，係一塊十分高質嘅牛扒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/221443_70e7904cb982d5d97fbdf4cade91d715.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F221443_70e7904cb982d5d97fbdf4cade91d715.jpg&h=a031dee7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/221444_70e7904cb982d5d97fbdf4cade91d715.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F221444_70e7904cb982d5d97fbdf4cade91d715.jpg&h=55c42743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後嘅甜品焦糖香蕉船伴玉桂蘋果，好味，但已經好飽了🙏🏻 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/221504_e7d4a793088f0c67dd73314db25b175f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F221504_e7d4a793088f0c67dd73314db25b175f.jpg&h=8337285a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總括嚟講，人均約$500 消費，可能有少少奢侈，不過的確係試到一啲重未食過又高質嘅菜式，過程仲可以一路研究係咩嚟，係一次好好嘅經歷👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻 <br />\n<br />\nTokyolima<br />\r\n地址: 中環擺花街18-20號地舖"},{"pid":"1739584bf51f6bf6034c36d556a37c4ed3a7d39f","tid":353390,"uid":28031,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:18:28.000Z","msg":"躝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4bb5e6291da347e809f8b3b6d7ac35f00b3e65","tid":353390,"uid":55419,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:19:41.000Z","msg":"妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你當我地唔識分廣告定食評咩"},{"pid":"af91068a29b4c8b010a80cd7789d630a9cffee7d","tid":353390,"uid":7867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:20:03.000Z","msg":"中環 日本飲品"},{"pid":"8637f151deae08c773aaf8cc0afea0914e8d1ded","tid":353390,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中環 日本飲品</blockquote><br />\n是日本人"},{"pid":"25ac3f83e0b791080e9f81212ed41c9576fe0c4e","tid":353390,"uid":104186,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:23:36.000Z","msg":"我都想係廣告🙈純粹搵地方推吓個fanpage lol"},{"pid":"420ecd2c20496c2e01f4a678893d4244d833c31d","tid":353390,"uid":29684,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:23:53.000Z","msg":"Where<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想食"},{"pid":"839b1bc58857d5e8d78688a427f5ea56ef66c21e","tid":353390,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bee801c8ca0c9c7e77805285d7c30a663312b424","tid":353390,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"食評黎講算打得幾詳細 每個dish都有提及 但未夠仔細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nH&amp;M stands for Hamachi and Maguro<br />\nMain dish black cod用左日式西京燒整法 所以甜啲但都好食<br />\n之後牛肉係配咩汁？介紹下"},{"pid":"57a0d7eabef7b0c60ddedb8b954206baaea7a95a","tid":353390,"uid":104186,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食評黎講算打得幾詳細 每個dish都有提及 但未夠仔細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nH&amp;M stands for Hamachi and Maguro<br />\nMain dish black cod用左日式西京燒整法 所以甜啲但都好食<br />\n之後牛肉係配咩汁？介紹下</blockquote><br />\n感謝🙏🏻 鐘意嘢食但唔係專家，所以好多位都係憑感覺寫🙉第一次出post 唔知係咪有咩規舉...<br />\n<br />\n牛肉都係配類似薄荷醬，但味道比Taco 淡口，牛肉味反而出好多，因為覺得料靚所以 2 個主菜我都係無乜沾汁食🙏🏻"},{"pid":"6f1bcbbabfe82e8251a80b506e96f72ac03f96d9","tid":353390,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30caa29087bf29d2d129ae6da1ebbbd40f502ebb","tid":353390,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食評黎講算打得幾詳細 每個dish都有提及 但未夠仔細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nH&amp;M stands for Hamachi and Maguro<br />\nMain dish black cod用左日式西京燒整法 所以甜啲但都好食<br />\n之後牛肉係配咩汁？介紹下</blockquote><br />\n感謝🙏🏻 鐘意嘢食但唔係專家，所以好多位都係憑感覺寫🙉第一次出post 唔知係咪有咩規舉...<br />\n<br />\n牛肉都係配類似薄荷醬，但味道比Taco 淡口，牛肉味反而出好多，因為覺得料靚所以 2 個主菜我都係無乜沾汁食🙏🏻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實呢個dish係滲入左日式元素<br />\n無記錯個堆係edamame puree毛豆蓉 再配左啲pickles<br />\n下次記住試清楚個汁 因為都係好緊要嘅環<br />\n坊間foodie好多 如果唔增值下自己對食物嘅專業知識只會流於表面 加油"},{"pid":"df66ae659d9714f7761982f150a8a59f1522d1e1","tid":353390,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:03:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食評黎講算打得幾詳細 每個dish都有提及 但未夠仔細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nH&amp;M stands for Hamachi and Maguro<br />\nMain d